## Merge History

| Component                 | Source             | Status     | Contribution                 |
| ------------------------- | ------------------ | ---------- | ---------------------------- |
| **Core 3-tier isolation** | KooshaPari/nanovms | вң… Complete | WASM/gVisor/Firecracker      |
| **AWS deployment**        | BytePort/nvms      | вң… Merged   | Firecracker orchestration    |
| **Unified interface**     | PhenoCompose       | вң… New      | Rust driver, standardization |

## Key Features

- **Multi-Tier Isolation Strategy** вҖ” Choose isolation level (WASM, gVisor, Firecracker) based on trust model and performance requirements
- **Unified Interface** вҖ” Single `pheno-compose` CLI for all isolation backends; configuration portable across tiers
- **Sub-Second Cold Starts** вҖ” WASM tier enables 1ms startup for rapid scaling and function-as-a-service workloads
- **Container Compatibility** вҖ” gVisor tier runs standard OCI containers without hardware virtualization
- **Full Virtualization** вҖ” Firecracker tier provides complete OS-level isolation for untrusted or legacy code
- **Resource Metering** вҖ” Track CPU, memory, I/O per workload with automatic enforcement
- **Networking** вҖ” Bridge or overlay network modes; DNS resolution via Phenotype service mesh
- **Volume Management** вҖ” Persistent volumes, ephemeral scratch, read-only root filesystem support
- **Observability** вҖ” Built-in logging, metrics (Prometheus), distributed tracing (Tempo integration)

## Platform Support

| Platform    | Tier 1 (WASM) | Tier 2 (gVisor) | Tier 3 (Firecracker)       |
| ----------- | ------------- | --------------- | -------------------------- |
| **macOS**   | вң… Native      | вң… Lima/VZ       | вң… Virtualization.framework |
| **Linux**   | вң… Native      | вң… Native        | вң… KVM                      |
| **Windows** | вң… Native      | вң… WSL2          | вң… WSL2                     |

## Installation

```bash
# Install NVMS
curl -fsSL https://get.nvms.dev | sh

# Or build from source
git clone https://github.com/KooshaPari/nvms.git
cd nvms && go build ./cmd/nvms

# Install PhenoCompose driver
cargo install pheno-compose --features nvms-driver
```

## Features

- **Multi-Tier Isolation** вҖ” WASM, gVisor, Firecracker for different trust/performance tradeoffs
- **Unified Orchestration** вҖ” PhenoCompose driver standardizes deployment across tiers
- **Cross-Platform** вҖ” Native support for macOS, Linux, Windows
- **Fast Startup** вҖ” WASM in milliseconds for dev/testing workloads
- **Secure Isolation** вҖ” gVisor/Firecracker for untrusted code execution

